{"type":null,"faqId":44790,"title":"如何不显示桌面图标上的数字？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">EMUI3.1系统支持此功能，操作路径：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">“桌面 &gt; 长按空白处(没有显示图标的区域)  &gt; 桌面设置 &gt; 图标角标”，可以关闭所有程序的角标提示，也可以选择性关闭。比如，不希望看到设置的角标，可以只关闭“设置”这一项。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161056\" style=\"width:2.6645834in;height:4.7458334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161057\" style=\"width:2.6743054in;height:4.7458334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161058\" style=\"width:2.3972223in;height:4.2381945in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"291","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-S